# Fusball Project

Phaser 4 + SvelteKit foosball game. Read `AGENTS.md` for full context.

## Stack

- Phaser 4.0.0 (Arcade physics), Svelte 5, SvelteKit, TypeScript, Vite
- Dev: `npm run dev` (port 8080). Build: `npm run build`

## Conventions

- Game logic in `src/game/` — Svelte is shell only (`PhaserGame.svelte`, `+page.svelte`)
- All dimensions/tuning in `src/game/config/gameConfig.ts`
- TS imports use `.js` suffix: `import { X } from "./Foo.js"`
- New scenes must `EventBus.emit("current-scene-ready", this)` in `create()`
- Prefer procedural `Graphics` over new assets for MVP placeholders
- Minimize scope — match existing entity/system split

## Do not

- Change `ssr = false` in `+layout.ts` without strong reason
- Hardcode table/stick/ball sizes outside `gameConfig.ts`
- Duplicate player2 stick config — use `getMirroredPlayerConfig()`
